assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: We.Connect SA designs, manufactures, assembles, and distributes computers, and peripheral and electronic equipment in France. Its products include computers; monitors; multimedia products; storage products, which include internal and external hard, SSD, and multimedia hard drives, as well as Wi-Fi storage devices. The company's products also consist of PC accessories, such as mouse, keyboard, luggage, gaming, and protection products; tablet accessories, such as cases, connectors, backup batteries, chargers, brackets, and tablets; smart phone accessories comprising cases and covers, screen protectors, connectors, backup batteries, chargers, and armbands; sport accessories, which include earphones, armbands, and belts, as well as outdoor products; telephone accessories, such as shells, armbands, headphone packs, etc.; and car accessories. In addition, it offers toys; gaming; light and sound; urban mobility; connectivity and charging products; and helmets, as well as warranty services. The company offers its products under the Rivertech, Gamium, Halterrego, HEDEN, Digital, Unika, Unika Pro, and WE brand names. Further, it engages in the custom PC design and assembly business; and provides technical support and after-sales services. We.Connect SA is headquartered in Paris, France.
